definition: luxuriant/buxom/variant of 豐|丰[feng1]/variant of 風|风[feng1]/appearance/charm

sentences.english: What a surprise of bumper harvest will the flowers bring us after they all are gone?
sentences.chinese: 繁花落尽，我们收获的又将是一份怎样的惊喜与丰盈？

sentences.english: Some books inspire and motivate us to do more with our lives.
sentences.chinese: 一些书籍鼓励和促使我们的生活变得更加丰盈。

sentences.english: From Thee have flowed, as from a pleasant river.
sentences.chinese: 浩如河江，流来活力何丰盈。

sentences.english: So… our lives fill out in goodness.
sentences.chinese: 因此，我们的生命在美善中丰盈。

sentences.english: China clothes fades to go, is a heart of plentiful Ying emotion.
sentences.chinese: 华裳褪去，是一颗丰盈感性的心。

sentences.english: Use in the bath or shower to create a foamy lather all over your body. Rinse off thoroughly.
sentences.chinese: 于浸浴或淋浴时使用，产生丰盈泡沫，用后冲洗干净。

sentences.english: In the fall season, everything comes together and you reap wonderful harvests of abundance.
sentences.chinese: 在这个成熟期，一起来收割丰盈美妙的一切收获。

sentences.english: Innovative technical formula can create full and charming lips make-up effect by slight application.
sentences.chinese: 创新技术配方，轻轻一抹缔造出更加丰盈魅惑的唇妆。

sentences.english: Let happiness as a carrier to measure whether life full of abundance.
sentences.chinese: 让幸福做一个载体去丈量人生是否饱满丰盈。

sentences.english: Young Mouton wines are wild as new world wines, but fruity.
sentences.chinese: 太早饮用的木桐就象新世界酒一样粗旷但果香丰盈。
